dc_title_s: Bombay guide map: including part of Salsette
dc_description_s: Survey of India. Alternate title: 1:25,000 Bombay guide map first edition. Relief shown by 20 feet contour interval and spot heights. Insets: Bombay and environs (1: 200,000); Index to districts municipalities & municipal wards. In lower left margin: "Reg. No. 3246H.D'45-2000'50. 1st edition 1945 July (Reprint of 1933 Edition)." In lower right margin: "Printed at the Survey of India Offices (H.L.O.).".
